Well it's been a few days and all I can say what a full circle moment playing 15 minutes away from where I grew up and saw my first concert when I was 15 years old. (Journey/Foreigner). Sad that my father couldn't see it in person but I'm sure he enjoyed the view from heaven and beyond happy my mother was able to see me play with Ice for the first time ever. Feeling extra blessed to have had so many friends come hang as well. You guys mean the world to me. ❤️. 
.
.
.
.
